quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  16,41,"Uye avo vakatama munzira yaAllah, mushure mekunge vatadzirwa (vadzvinyirirwa), zvirokwazvo, tichavapa pekugara pakanaka pano pasi, asi muripo wehupenyu hunotevera wakakura chaizvo dai vachiziva"
  16,42,Avo vakatsungirira (pasi pano) uye vakaisa vimbo yavo kuna Tenzi vavo
  16,43,Uye hatina kutumira (sevatumwa) kumashure kwako (Muhammad (SAW)) asi varume vataitumira mashoko. Bvunzai (imi vanonamata zvidhori) avo vanoziva Magwaro (Torah neVhangeri) kana musingazivi
  16,44,"Nezviratidzo zviri pachena neMagwaro (Takatuma vatumwa). Uye takatumira kwauri (Muhammad (SAW)) yeuchidzo (Qur’aan), kuti utsanangurire vanhu zviri pachena zvatumirwa kwavari, uye kuti zvimwe vangafunge"
  16,45,"Avo vanopangana zvakaipa vanonzwa kuchengetedzeka here kuti Allah havavanyudzi pasi, kana kuti marwadzo haavabati kubva kune mativi avasingatarisiri"
  16,46,"Kana kuti achavabata pakati pekuenda nekudzoka (kumabasa avo), kuti pasave nekupukunyuka kwavari (kubva kune mutongo waAllah)"
  16,47,"Kana kuti achavabata (achavaparadza) zvishoma nezvishoma (muhupenyu nehupfumi hwavo)? Zvirokwazvo, Tenzi venyu vazere nenyasha netsitsi"
  16,48,"Havana kuona here izvo zvakasikwa naAllah kubva kune zvese, mimvuri yazvo inorerekera kurudyi nekuruboshwe zvichipfugamira Allah, uye ndevepasi"
  16,49,"Uye Allah vanopfugamirwa nezvinhu zvese zviri kudenga nepasi, kubva kumhuka nengirozi, uye havazvitutumadzi"
  16,50,"Vanotya Tenzi vavo vari pamusoro pavo, uye vanoita zvavanenge vakomekedzwa"